    "Xu et al. (2021) proposed Gan Dialect and Hakka DSR system based on the attention mechanism, which used CNN and BiLSTM to extract dialect features, respectively.",
    "The experiment results showed that the performance based on the attention dialect recognition model outperformed the DNN model.",
    "Besides, Liu et al. (2020) presented the Datong dialect speech translation system based on the attention mechanism.",
    "When they compared the attention mechanism with the cascade model, it was shown that the proposed Chinese DSR not only saved time cost but also effectively improved accuracy.",
    "The attention mechanism is often combined with neural networks to identify Chinese dialects."
